{"tid":827561,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"恐怖故事","createTime":"2018-09-19T04:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T02:37:58.000Z","uid":82482,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"57ea2d946436ffdf52650aea975e4b79b07ae869","tid":827561,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T04:25:14.000Z","msg":"有無聽過午夜十二點唔可以沖涼的故事？<br />\n<br />\n話説徐婆婆已經年屆九十，佢好清楚，如果要沖涼不能在午夜十二點，當年隔壁的老王就因為犯禁，最後響浴室跣親搞到撼親個頭，爆哂缸。<br />\n<br />\n而今晚，徐婆婆正發燒，胡喱胡塗就踏正十二點走去沖涼，恐怖既事咁就發生咗，原來佢忘記咗開燈！今次要摸黑洗身要彎腰執返上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366a66180f59b794c741c242aa7396698dfa0bb2","tid":827561,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"是咪驚到瀨屎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd44ca2c6f0e4c9a041fc103369782384716b045","tid":827561,"uid":254117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"6uo"},{"pid":"632c7dd2379541808374bb73d5f15d76c7378d23","tid":827561,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:30:56.000Z","msg":"到底有冇人睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30e13d5f44e08fa419420b88cf74207432a37d2","tid":827561,"uid":193871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T02:37:58.000Z","msg":"#3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}